{"tid":1822965,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁美芬促政府考慮直接宣布實施國歌法","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T02:34:47.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1027398be707238010d5a1a112fe3eef9bb7fb4d","tid":1822965,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"立法會議員梁美芬提出，如果反對派要拖垮國歌法本地立法工作，政府應該考慮根據基本法，直接宣布在本港實施國歌法。民主派就認為，國歌法必須要經過本地立法。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，會適時恢復國歌法在立法會二讀辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502141-20200110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502141-20200110.htm&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=4b5cb2a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502141-20200110.htm&h=7556335d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502141-20200110.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a7652ce9d34b331a197fdc4c31595af953ae8dfe","tid":1822965,"uid":27250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"順便宣布一國兩制已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a32cb6a4037ef365f21fbb9bbb9e2aaaaa01398","tid":1822965,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=66b37626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n